        <bioghist id="ref12">
            <head>Historical Note</head>
            <p>The Blacksburg [Virginia] Regional Arts Association (BRAA) was founded in 1950 as a chapter of the Virginia Museum of Fine Arts. BRAA sponsored monthly exhibits at the Virginia Tech Library and brought Virginia Museum Artmobiles to Blacksburg.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref1">
